ius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🌲 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas.com%2Frobotics%2Fu1-worlds-first-mass-produced-humanoid-robot%2F\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/54986bd/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2700x1418+0+49/resize/1200x630!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com%2F35%2F72%2Fa0d922a34303ad5fd6e70e548e73%2Fccafe040dec2ce46521caf79168bb91e.jpg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/54986bd/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2700x1418+0+49/resize/1200x630!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com%2F35%2F72%2Fa0d922a34303ad5fd6e70e548e73%2Fccafe040dec2ce46521caf79168bb91e.jpg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p><img alt=\"A male version of the Uworld U1 struts its stuff\" src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/8cf5884/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2700x1516+0+0/resize/1440x809!/format/webp/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com%2F35%2F72%2Fa0d922a34303ad5fd6e70e548e73%2Fccafe040dec2ce46521caf79168bb91e.jpg\" /><p>People have been fantasizing about humanoid robots for decades. Movies such as Blade Runner, Ex Machina, and A.I. Artificial Intelligence imagined a future where robots and AI could interact with humans and save them from loneliness. Today, those sci-fi stories seem to be closer to reality than ever before, as Chinese company Ubtech has recently launched a product it calls the world’s first full-size, mass-produced \"ultrabionic\" companion robot.</p><p><a href=\"https://newatlas.com/robotics/u1-worlds-first-mass-produced-humanoid-robot/\">Continue Reading</a></p><p><b>Category:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/robotics/\">Robotics</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/engineering/\">Engineering</a></p><p><b>Tags:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/humanoid/\" rel=\"tag\">Humanoid</a></p>",
